Release:	2%{?dist}
Summary:	Globus Toolkit - Globus XIO UDT Driver

Group:		System Environment/Libraries
License:	ASL 2.0
URL:		http://www.globus.org/
Source:		http://www.globus.org/ftppub/gt5/5.2/testing/packages/src/%{_name}-%{version}.tar.gz
